OL,3,CPSNI and Met investigate email sent to
OL,4,CNI schools
OL,6,FA number of schools across Northern
OL,7,FIreland have been closed due to
OL,8,Fsecurity concerns.
OL,10,FThere have been reports of nine
OL,11,Fschools in counties Antrim, Tyrone and
OL,12,FFermanagh. Some schools posted
OL,13,Fmessages on social media advising
OL,14,Fparents that they had closed.
OL,16,FThere have been reports of 'security
OL,17,Fconcerns'.
OL,19,FPolice said it was due to an email
OL,20,Fsent to schools and they were working
OL,21,Fwith the Metropolitan Police in London.
