OL,6,FThe Education Authority referred press
OL,7,Fqueries to the PSNI.
OL,9,FNorth Antrim MP Jim Allister said:
OL,10,F"Appalling to see NI schools closed
OL,11,Fbecause of a security threat,
OL,12,Fincluding Cross & Passion College in
OL,13,FBallycastle in North Antrim.
OL,15,F"I trust the police get on top of this
OL,16,Fsituation quickly and that concerns of
OL,17,Fparents, staff and pupils can be
OL,18,Fallayed."
