OL,3,CPSNI and Met investigate email sent to
OL,4,CNI schools
OL,6,FIn a social media post, DUP MLA Gary
OL,7,FMiddleton said: "Concerning that
OL,8,Fschools across NI have been affected
OL,9,Fby a security threat.
OL,11,F"An update from the PSNI and Education
OL,12,FAuthority is due to be issued shortly."
OL,14,FIn Fermanagh, there were reports of
OL,15,Fthree school closures.
OL,17,FIn an update Erne Integrated College
OL,18,Fopened saying police had given the all
OL,19,Fclear.
