OL,3,CPSNI and Met investigate email sent to
OL,4,CNI schools
OL,6,FThree schools in the Strabane area
OL,7,Fhave closed including Strabane
OL,8,FAcademy, Strabane Primary and Holy
OL,9,FCross College.
OL,11,FHoly Cross College posted on social
OL,12,Fmedia: "Unfortunately the school has
OL,13,Fto close today due to a security
OL,14,Fconcern.
OL,16,F"Any children already en route, we
OL,17,Fwould ask that parents make
OL,18,Farrangements to collect them. We will
OL,19,Fupdate you all as soon as possible
OL,20,Fthis morning."
