OL,3,CPSNI and Met investigate email sent to
OL,4,CNI schools
OL,6,FThe same message was posted on the
OL,7,FFacebook account of Cross and Passion
OL,8,FCollege in Ballycastle, Co Antrim.
OL,10,FThe PSNI statement said: "Police
OL,11,Freceived reports today, Monday 24
OL,12,FMarch, of an email sent to a number of
OL,13,Fschools in Enniskillen, Strabane and
OL,14,FBallycastle. As a result of this
OL,15,Femail, we are conducting enquiries,
OL,16,Fand liaising with the schools in
OL,17,Fquestion and also with the
OL,18,FMetropolitan Police in London."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
